![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e9948fc2-cc98-4bbe-a130-facfcea6b0da/49949.png?format=original)

Jacob Fatu was seen limping at the WWE Live Event in Great Britain. [PWInsider reports](https://pwinsider.com/article/208353/jacob-fatu-update.html?p=1) that Fatu legitimately suffered an injury, revealed by the newer outlet False Finish to be a back injury.

[Cory Hays](https://x.com/i/status/2060465296570307014), formerly the top WWE scooper at Bodyslam now at False Finish, reports WWE officials are assuming Fatu will be fine by The Clash in Italy Premium Live Event for his main event TRIBAL COMBAT match with Roman Reigns

But they are looking into alternative options in case Fatu is not medically cleared in time.